---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import headshot from "../assets/cory-headshot.png";
---

<section class="section-y">
  <div class="container-page grid gap-x-12 gap-y-8 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_minmax(0,1.6fr)] md:items-start">
    <div>
      <Image
        src={headshot}
        alt="Cory, the human behind Mainstay"
        width={280}
        height={285}
        loading="lazy"
        class="border-line mb-6 aspect-square w-[180px] rounded-[var(--radius-card)] border object-cover shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] sm:w-[220px] md:w-[260px]"
      />
      <p class="text-ink-mute text-sm tracking-wide uppercase mb-3">
        About
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-[clamp(1.75rem,3.5vw,2.25rem)] leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.01em] text-balance max-w-[14ch]">
        Hi — I'm Cory.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-[52ch] space-y-5 text-[1.0625rem] leading-[1.65] text-ink-soft text-pretty">
      <p>
        I started Mainstay because the local shops I love most kept
        ending up with the worst websites. Templates that fight back. Big
        agencies that won't take a $1,500 job. Family members who built
        something nice in 2014 and then went to college.
      </p>
      <p>
        I've spent years building software for companies of every size, and
        I wanted to spend the next chunk of it making real websites for
        people I'd recognize on Main Street. One shop at a time. Honest
        prices, in writing. The work done by the person you'd call.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you've got a shop and a few minutes, I'd love to hear about it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
